//! Experimental: casting helpers.
//!
//! Contains helper functions to cast values between primitive types.
//!
//! APIs in this module are unstable and subject to change.

/// This entire module is only experimental. I want to gather my thoughts
/// on how to implement all the various cast operations.
//! Cast `value` to `T` using a static/unchecked cast (experimental).
public extern static_cast<T>(value: U) -> T;
//! Remove constness from a `&const T`, returning a mutable reference (unsafe).
public extern const_cast<T>(value: &const T) -> &T;